    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2003-06-12</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2003-08-25T13:54:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Veterans Nursing Home Care Act of 2003 - Requires the Secretary of Veterans Affairs to provide nursing home care to: (1) any veteran for a service-connected disability (current law); and (2) any veteran in need of such care who has a service-connected disability rated at ten (currently 70) percent or more. Eliminates the termination date for such requirement (December 31, 2003).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
